HEADWORD: Ascription
<hw>As*crip"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ascriptio</ets>, fr. <ets>ascribere</ets>. See
<er>Ascribe</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of ascribing, imputing, or
